    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example delivers crisp, linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The dual-VANOS system has been recently overhauled to ensure optimal valve timing, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to maintain chassis rigidity. Suspension performance is sharpened by Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, allowing the factory limited-slip differential to put power down with precision. While the exterior shows minor age-appropriate patina, the mechanical vitals and drivetrain synchronization remain excellent for the spirited purist.",
